WEBVTT

00:06.048 --> 00:08.050
[♪♪♪]

00:17.727 --> 00:19.812
♪ Young man goes out ♪

00:19.938 --> 00:25.234
♪ Looking for the diamond in the sea ♪

00:28.362 --> 00:32.450
♪ Old man rows his boat to shore ♪

00:32.533 --> 00:36.704
♪ And falls on twisted knees ♪

00:38.748 --> 00:45.463
